      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy verification using manufactured solutions must be demonstrated for all governing equations active in the hemolysis simulation.",
      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions applied to continuity and momentum equations; scalar transport equation for hemolysis species verified to first-order only. Required second-order verification not achieved for scalar transport. Achieved level 3."
