      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation-based grid convergence index (GCI) must be below 5% for NIH at all five operating points on at least three systematically refined meshes.",
      "rationale": "GCI computed on three mesh refinements; GCI below 5% at three of five operating points. At 6 L/min and 3200 RPM the GCI reaches 9.2%, indicating insufficient spatial resolution in the impeller tip-clearance region. Achieved level 3."
    },
