      "rationale": "The observational study used the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry and porcine blood analogue, matching the COU geometry and fluid. However, the retrospective observational design cannot confirm that confounding clinical variables were absent, reducing relevance score relative to a prospective controlled experiment. Achieved level 3 against required level 5."
